{"tid":2447154,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"六人受壓退選 浸大學生會斷莊","createTime":"2021-03-15T04:21:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-15T05:35:22.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d6f2f5fc92d199fbcdb639934f5d63fb40dadd9c","tid":2447154,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T04:21:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210315/3JO4ZCKL5NDNVN7RVDHEH2ZEJA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210315%2F3JO4ZCKL5NDNVN7RVDHEH2ZEJA%2F&d=qonCz35ufBxMHQAS3tFcDvzGhZJjjhZ%2BTSWVZI8Eykc%3D&h=a0e06474\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210315%2F3JO4ZCKL5NDNVN7RVDHEH2ZEJA%2F&h=74988a72\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210315/3JO4ZCKL5NDNVN7RVDHEH2ZEJA/</a><br />\n<br />\n六人受壓退選 浸大學生會斷莊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Y8P6o4zawsnkY2kYSsqh-REc9vo=/1000x562/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3GERPN25ENGWXAXUQMZY3MTSWE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FY8P6o4zawsnkY2kYSsqh-REc9vo%3D%2F1000x562%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3GERPN25ENGWXAXUQMZY3MTSWE.jpg&h=8ece9fbf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■浸大學生會候選內閣「獅誓」六名成員日前退選，內閣隨即喪失選舉資格。浸大學生會編委fb圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】國安法下學界人人自危。繼早前香港中文大學學生會總辭風波後，同屬「本土莊」的浸會大學學生會補選唯一候選內閣「獅誓」，當中六名成員日前突然退選，內閣隨即喪失選舉資格。該內閣候選幹事長朱慧盈解釋，有成員因受到壓力退選，她重申仍有參選意欲，不排除未來再次組閣參選。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n成員憂人身安全<br />\n<br />\n浸大學生會補選委員。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n朱慧盈昨日回覆本報查詢時稱，近日有成員從各方渠道接獲消息，稱有人打算對「獅誓」成員及理工大學學生會施壓，有成員因感到人身安全受威脅，內閣最終在成員意見分歧下退選。朱慧盈拒絕透露相關消息是否來自校方或警方國安處，亦拒絕透露訊息的具體內容。未有退選的朱慧盈稱仍有意服務同學，不排除未來組閣再參選。<br />\n<br />\n不過。。。。。。。。葉梓賢稱本學年不會再舉行補選，相信來年才會重新舉辦學生會選舉，意味浸大學生會今年「斷莊」。<br />\n<br />\n理大學。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n港版國安法陰霾下，多間大學的學生會均無人參選。中大學生會當選內閣「朔夜」早前以成員收到死亡恐嚇及校方圖株連其他學生組織為由，上任當天宣佈總辭。"},{"pid":"3059e745ee57a15e06210fef40761761f1cb3213","tid":2447154,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T04:23:10.000Z","msg":"朱慧盈拒絕透露相關消息是否來自校方或警方國安處，亦拒絕透露訊息的具體內容。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19569be8cbd759d07fec5c7cfbab73da48b26547","tid":2447154,"uid":311701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T04:23:26.000Z","msg":"骨牌效應<br />\n一国兩制<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f07b4e0450a1a481a4c43a5aefd19b0dbbec290","tid":2447154,"uid":33222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T04:25:55.000Z","msg":"好慘&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n大學上莊已變10年以上代價"},{"pid":"a24f6ada30aa2f45fa6f514a950e926dbfae09dd","tid":2447154,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T04:27:06.000Z","msg":"除非解放軍撤出香港，唔係學生會已玩完"},{"pid":"8501bb13f4f9806b593c27fade3ecc879245a7ef","tid":2447154,"uid":310817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T04:39:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a31526d62aceec888f8a789b3f65fc93c603d6d4","tid":2447154,"uid":168492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T05:28:17.000Z","msg":"港版國安法陰霾下，多間大學的學生會均無人參選。中大學生會當選內閣「朔夜」早前以成員收到死亡恐嚇及校方圖株連其他學生組織為由，上任當天宣佈總辭。<br />\n<br />\n由學校開始換血<br />\n好似master phd都已經好多支支"},{"pid":"fcc2495c4f71f4bf8bd67b9ba1f2f9fdaa50b2e2","tid":2447154,"uid":283240,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T05:33:50.000Z","msg":"成班傻仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  垃圾選你老母<br />\n<br />\n唔滿意咪去搗亂囉，廢青最拿手咖啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e829aa8d2e6a04ddd3cb73d64bb531b398d63d44","tid":2447154,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T05:35:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}